dotphiles
=========

dotfiles, ready to go

   *zsh*
   *bash*
   *vim*

INSTALLATION:
=============

### Quickstart

    git clone --recursive git@github.com:dotfiles/dotfiles.git ~/.dotfiles
    ./.dotfiles/dotsync/bin/dotsync -L

Sign up for an account on github, and click 

### Fork

Sign up for an account on [github][1] and click fork

    git clone --recursive git@github.com:username/dotfiles.git ~/.dotfiles
    ./.dotfiles/dotsync/bin/dotsync -L

Configuration
=============

### Zsh

Add your own settings to *zshrc*, *zshenv*, *zlogin*, *zlogout* and *zprofile*

### Git

Add your name, email and gpg keyid to *gitconfig*

### Dotsync

Add your dotfiles and machine names to *dotsyncrc*

